text: Ianoș Brînză (born 12 September 1998) is a Moldovan professional footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Liga I club Politehnica Iași, on loan from FC Botoșani. Brînză started his career at Dacia Chișinău, then played for Politehnica Iași, before signing for FC Botoșani in the summer of 2017. ==References== ==External links== * * * Ianoș Brînză at lpf.ro Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Chișinău Category:Moldovan footballers Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Moldovan National Division players Category:FC Dacia Chișinău players Category:Liga I players Category:FC Politehnica Iași (2010) players Category:FC Botoșani players Category:Liga II players Category:FC Petrolul Ploiești players Category:Moldovan expatriate footballers Category:Moldovan expatriate sportspeople in Romania Category:Expatriate footballers in Romania
